Package: interactionHub
Type: Package
Version: 0.0.1
Title: A R/Bioconductor package to detect the interaction hub from
       HiC/HiChIP/HiCAR data
Authors@R: c(person(given="Jianhong", family="Ou", email="jianhong.ou@duke.edu", 
        role=c("aut", "cre")),
        person(given="Yarui", family="Diao", role="fnd"))
Maintainer: Jianhong Ou <jianhong.ou@duke.edu>
Description: The interactionHub package can import interactions from bedpe file
        and define the interaction hubs, the hot interaction spots. The detected
        interaction hubs will be annotated and enrich analized for downstream
        validation.
License: file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0), stats
Imports: AnnotationDbi, graph, GO.db, 
        GenomicRanges, GenomeInfoDb, GenomicFeatures,
        methods,
        IRanges,
        RBGL,
        S4Vectors
Suggests: RUnit, BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown, rtracklayer, testthat,
        TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.knownGene, org.Hs.eg.db
URL: https://github.com/jianhong/interactionHub
BugReports: https://github.com/jianhong/interactionHub/issues
biocViews: Visualization
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Encoding: UTF-8
